---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Lab Bench">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>The Lab Bench</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Personal hardware builds, control systems, and enterprise infrastructure.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <div class="card-grid">

    <!-- PROXMOX & INFRASTRUCTURE CARD -->
    <a href="/projects/homelab" class="card-link">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Proxmox Infrastructure & Edge Compute</h3>
        <p>A virtualized compute node hosting Home Assistant OS, Ollama LLMs (Qwen), and self-hosted services behind NGINX (*.lab.jbfueston.com). Network traffic is governed via Router-on-a-Stick 802.1Q VLAN trunking and OPNsense firewalling.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Proxmox VE</span>
          <span class="tag">Home Assistant</span>
          <span class="tag">Local AI (Qwen)</span>
          <span class="tag">Router-on-a-Stick</span>
          <span class="tag">VLAN 10/99</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- WIRELESS SIGNAL AUDIT RIG CARD -->
    <a href="/projects/argus" class="card-link">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Wireless Signal Audit Rig</h3>
        <p>Custom portable hardware suite designed for RF spectral analysis and mapping wireless network density. The build focuses on high-gain antenna integration and real-time data visualization.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">RF Analysis</span>
          <span class="tag">Hardware Integration</span>
          <span class="tag">Signal Processing</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- AUTOMATED AQUAPONICS SYSTEM CARD -->
    <a href="/projects/aquaponics" class="card-link">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Passive Aquaponics & Biosphere Control</h3>
        <p>A space-constrained Deep Water Culture (DWC) aquaponics system focusing on passive nutrient cycling, spatial design constraints, and telemetries via ESP32 environmental sensors.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Biological Systems</span>
          <span class="tag">Nutrient Cycling</span>
          <span class="tag">ESP32 Telemetry</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div> <!-- CARD-GRID CLOSES HERE NOW -->
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-main); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .divider { border: 0; height: 1px; background: #eee; margin: 2rem 0; }

  /* Grid Layout */
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background: #f0f4f8;
    color: #0b3c5d;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>